{"tid":1170506,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃台仰　走達賴熱比婭路線　在外　關注人權　著力維持身份認同","createTime":"2019-05-25T04:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T04:53:44.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5f4abb88a5e4bd7bb3f6cf886c7077994efc2b47","tid":1170506,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T04:49:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.france24.com/en/20190522-hong-kong-independence-activists-granted-refugee-status-germany\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2F20190522-hong-kong-independence-activists-granted-refugee-status-germany&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62O%2FcXzH0lQqBACTLtzCSRXY%3D&h=e78cd036\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.france24.com/en/20190522-hong-kong-independence-activists-granted-refugee-status-germany</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F2dON3G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF2dON3G.png&h=2c0ee24b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃台仰：<br />\n現在我不提倡香港獨立，我認為對香港最重要的是其人權狀況。<br />\n<br />\n第二，是我們的身份認同。如果我們喪失我們的身份認同，香港人的存在就會消失。<br />\n<br />\nWhile abroad, Wong said<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Now I won't advocate Hong Kong independence. I think the most important thing for Hong Kong is its human rights situation.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Secondly, it's our identity. If we lost our identity, Hong Kong people will disappear in the game.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCPForum/posts/3003853476299466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCPForum%2Fposts%2F3003853476299466&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62O%2FcXzH0lQqBACTLtzCSRXY%3D&h=8af66216\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCPForum/posts/3003853476299466</a><br />\n<br />\nRFA 黃台仰在2017 訪問中預示香港好快會被同化為一個中國城市。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1wQhvo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1wQhvo.png&h=967637a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iaXzKas.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiaXzKas.png&h=f0aa1632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1122338686706651136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1122338686706651136&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62O%2FcXzH0lQqBACTLtzCSRXY%3D&h=ff665634\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1122338686706651136&h=6fc24e40\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1122338686706651136</a><br />\n<br />\n這是分三個進路：第一推動香港獨立；第二使自身繼續存在，雖然做的不是香港獨立，但就算一時做不了獨立，只要繼續存在，都可以再推動；第三是記錄，記錄想法、事情，記錄好，就算有此想法的人都消亡，都可以給予後來再起者支援，就像胡斯、馬文輝。"},{"pid":"885988ee4c13327369ec701a4d3c93a05bf4a2fe","tid":1170506,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T04:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞個全球港人大會？"}]}